We watched all the Portlandia shows tonight. All I can say is: this is EXACTLY what Portland is like. It was weird seeing what the people from out of town were laughing at that the natives were just like, "Well, yeah. That happens."

I have a Bravia Blu-Ray player which has Amazon, Netflix and Hulu all on it - freaking has changed my life. I love it. I've tried very hard to not torrent/Usenet stuff these days and this is the first time where I felt that policy hasn't made my life worse.
